  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, as a <em>standard action</em> once per day, you can shout a cry instilled with the noble sacrifices of your ancestor. You and any allies within 30 feet who can hear you gain a +1 <em>morale bonus</em> on attack and damage rolls for a number of rounds equal to half your <em>sorcerer</em> level (minimum 1). At 7th level and every four levels thereafter, this bonus increases by +1, to a maximum of +5 at 19th level.</p>"
